1
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:47,320
Hello.

2
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,120
Room 1914, Kaijia Building.

3
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,680
There is a safe there.

4
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,680
Find a passport inside.

5
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:54,940
The name on the passport is Jessica Alba.

6
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,960
You have 24 hours.

7
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,400
I'll send you their company's

8
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:00,600
surveillance videos from the past few days later.

9
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,640
And after I get it?

10
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:04,319
I'll tell you what to do then.

11
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,560
Li, how is it going?

12
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,089
Calculate the return rate.

13
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,320
Hello. Where are you delivering this?

14
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,450
Zhengtong Finance.

15
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,080
We're having a meeting inside.

16
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:26,880
It's not convenient for you to go in.

17
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,640
Tell you what.

18
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,240
I'll deliver it for you,

19
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,560
and bring the empty bottle back in a bit.

20
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,490
Okay, thank you.

21
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,440
Sir,

22
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:45,280
I only borrowed 8,000 originally.

23
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:47,280
I've already paid back over 10,000.

24
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:49,100
How can I still owe over 6,000?

25
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,260
Isn't there interest?

26
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,920
If you don't pay up,

27
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,400
those photos of you will be leaked,

28
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,040
and your classmates and family will find out.

29
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,800
Then...

30
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,400
No, no.

31
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,080
Sir,

32
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,520
I really have no other way.

33
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,960
Please help me.

34
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,000
Since you're so pretty,

35
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,970
You should be able to handle it.

36
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,680
Welcome.

37
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,730
What would you like?

38
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,320
Officer Shao.

39
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,490
I've turned over a new leaf.

40
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,960
I stopped picking locks a long time ago.

41
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,400
This is what I do now.

42
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,440
You two are still doing this?

43
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,360
Officer Shao.

44
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,560
You know about my sister's condition.

45
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,360
She can't grow taller

46
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,680
and will always look like a child.

47
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,340
It's hard for her to find a job.

48
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,360
This is absolutely the last time.

49
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,360
Please let us off.

50
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,730
We'll leave right away.

51
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,730
Don't panic.

52
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,960
I'm looking for you two for something else.

53
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,320
Can you and your sister do me a favor?

54
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,040
Got it.

55
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,970
Whose phone is this?

56
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,320
Hello, I lost my phone.

57
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,080
Can I borrow your phone to make a call?

58
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,720
Sure.

59
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,640
Okay, thank you.

60
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,570
You're welcome.

61
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,040
Hello.

62
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,560
Hi,

63
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,840
did you find my phone?

64
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,080
Okay.

65
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:14,010
Wait a moment, I'll be right there.

66
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,480
Solve this problem as soon as possible.

67
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,200
Go.

68
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,120
Come in.

69
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,960
Thank you for trusting Ansu Insurance.

70
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,890
Here is our new insurance package.

71
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,140
Please take a look.

72
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,520
No need.

73
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,600
I asked you to come here

74
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,800
for something else.

75
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,200
Have you seen a movie

76
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:39,400
about a man who stole something,

77
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,120
was chased with nowhere to run,

78
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,520
and hid in an unfinished building?

79
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:46,720
He hid the item in an air duct on the first floor.

80
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,540
After he got out of prison,

81
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:52,080
he found the building had become a police station.

82
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,159
In order to get his stuff back,

83
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:56,159
he sneaked into the police station.

84
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,570
But my luck is a little better than his.

85
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:01,120
This building became an insurance company.

86
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,400
You must be joking.

87
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,280
Let me go get my stuff back.

88
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,120
If I can't get it back,

89
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,320
If I can't get it back,

90
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,920
you can call the police.

91
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,080
If I get it back,

92
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:17,880
If I get it back,

93
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,000
I'll give you half.

94
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:23,480
Does selling insurance really make you a lot of money?

95
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,200
What the hell is this?

96
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:15,920
What is it?

97
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:19,760
It's normal to have cockroaches.

98
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,000
What is this?

99
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,840
It's so big.

100
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,960
Did you call for pest control?

101
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,440
No.

102
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,200
Maybe Long called them.

103
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,360
Just deal with it quickly.

104
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:33,920
Okay.

105
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,360
I'll get going now.

106
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,160
The pesticide is harmless to humans,

107
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,840
but it has a smell.

108
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,280
You'd better step outside.

109
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,440
How long will it take?

110
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,960
About 15 minutes.

111
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,520
Okay, get it done quickly.

112
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,160
Okay.

113
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:50,560
Okay.

114
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:53,040
Peel off this protective film and it's ready to use.

115
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,760
Contact us if you need anything.

116
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,400
Okay.

117
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,700
Didn't get to use such a big suitcase.

118
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,920
This is for other pests.

119
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:07,320
Hello, sir.

120
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,250
Did you call for an errand service?

121
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,170
Yes, deliver something for me.

122
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,040
Sure.

123
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:45,800
Lighting Team.
